com.stripe.android.model

Class PersonTokenParams

  • TokenParams
    • com.stripe.android.model.PersonTokenParams
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    StripeParamsModel

    public class PersonTokenParams
extends TokenParams

    Creates a single-use token that represents the details for a person. Use this when creating or updating persons associated with a Connect account. See the documentation to learn more.

    See Create a person token

    the documentation, Create a person token

        Creates a single-use token that represents the details for a person. Use this when creating or updating persons associated with a Connect account. See the documentation to learn more.

        See Create a person token

        Parameters:
        address -

        The person’s address.

        person.address

        addressKana -

        The Kana variation of the person’s address (Japan only).

        person.address_kana

        addressKanji -

        The Kanji variation of the person’s address (Japan only).

        person.address_kanji

        dateOfBirth -

        The person’s date of birth.

        person.dob

        email -

        The person’s email address.

        person.email

        firstName -

        The person’s first name.

        person.first_name

        firstNameKana -

        The Kana variation of the person’s first name (Japan only).

        person.first_name_kana

        firstNameKanji -

        The Kanji variation of the person’s first name (Japan only).

        person.first_name_kanji

        gender -

        The person’s gender (International regulations require either “male” or “female”).

        person.gender

        idNumber -

        The person’s ID number, as appropriate for their country. For example, a social security number in the U.S., social insurance number in Canada, etc. Instead of the number itself, you can also provide a PII token.

        person.id_number

        lastName -

        The person’s last name.

        person.last_name

        lastNameKana -

        The Kana variation of the person’s last name (Japan only).

        person.last_name_kana

        lastNameKanji -

        The Kanji variation of the person’s last name (Japan only).

        person.last_name_kanji

        maidenName -

        The person’s maiden name.

        person.maiden_name

        metadata -

        Set of key-value pairs that you can attach to an object. This can be useful for storing additional information about the object in a structured format. Individual keys can be unset by posting an empty value to them. All keys can be unset by posting an empty value to metadata.

        person.metadata

        phone -

        The person’s phone number.

        person.phone

        relationship -

        The relationship that this person has with the account’s legal entity.

        person.relationship

        ssnLast4 -

        The last 4 digits of the person’s social security number.

        person.ssn_last_4

        verification -

        The person’s verification status.

        person.verification

        the documentation, Create a person token
